<L>__{exterior balcony, chieko's apartment night}
<D>__{she opens the door to the balcony and points at the void: it's over twelve floors. kenji looks over; the distance is dizzying. chieko writes in her notebook and shows him the piece of paper.}
<C>__{kenji}
<D>__{you saw her jump? she nods and writes again. she looks perturbed.}
<C>__{kenji }
<D>__{you've already told the other officers? she nods again. kenji holds her by her arms.}
<C>__{kenji }
<D>__{i don't know what you're talking about. chieko remains motionless for a few seconds. she scrawls in her notebook "then why do you want to talk to my father?" kenji reads and then turns to her.}
<C>__{kenji }
<D>__{it's about a hunting rifle in his name. the red bulb on the gadget starts to blink. chieko spots it from the balcony and signals to kenji that she has to go to the kitchen. she runs off.}
